@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<h1 class="h2">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<main>
    <p>Effective Date: <em class="text-muted">February 24, 2025</em></p>

    <h2 class="h5">1. Introduction</h2>
    <p>Welcome to <strong>Blackjack</strong>! Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, store, and protect your information when you use our application.</p>
    <p>By using Blackjack, you agree to the collection and use of information as outlined in this policy. If you do not agree, please refrain from using the application.</p>

    <h2 class="h5">2. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We collect the following types of information:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Username</strong> (if you create an account)</li>
        <li><strong>Email Address</strong> (if you create an account)</li>
        <li><strong>Name</strong> (optional, if provided by the user)</li>
        <li><strong>Gameplay Data</strong> (such as scores, achievements, and play history)</li>
    </ul>
    <p>If you choose to play as a guest, we do not collect personally identifiable information.</p>

    <h2 class="h5">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>We use your information to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Provide and maintain your account (if applicable)</li>
        <li>Improve gameplay features and user experience</li>
        <li>Store game progress and history for returning users</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="h5">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>Blackjack does not use third-party services such as analytics, advertising networks, or external payment processors.</p>

    <h2 class="h5">5. User Accounts and Guest Play</h2>
    <p>Users can create an account to save progress or play as a guest. Guest players will not have their data stored beyond the current session.</p>

    <h2 class="h5">6. Data Storage and Security</h2>
    <p>User data is stored securely in a cloud database. We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure.</p>

    <h2 class="h5">7. Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>We <strong>do not</strong> share user data with third parties. Your information remains private and is used solely for the functionality of the game.</p>

    <h2 class="h5">8. Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>Blackjack is not intended for users under the age of 13. If you are a parent or guardian and believe your child has provided personal information, please contact us for data deletion.</p>

    <h2 class="h5">9. User Rights and Data Deletion</h2>
    <p>Users can delete their accounts at any time, which will permanently remove all associated data from our database. Once deleted, this data cannot be recovered.</p>

    <h2 class="h5">10. Contact Information</h2>
    <p>For any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us at: <a href="mailto:support.bjack25@yahoo.com">support.bjack25@yahoo.com</a></p>
</main>